wikipedia_page.main: Henry Edward Hugh "Harry" Blakeney (8 October 1890 – 12 February 1958) was a British track and field athlete who competed in the 1912 Summer Olympics.In 1912 he was eliminated in the semi-finals of the 110 metre hurdles competition. In the 100 metres event he was eliminated in the first round.
